activities.activityName: Go to a museum date with partner

Event though it's forbiden, we managed to take pics with every painting in the museum!
THEY KNEEL INTO THE FLOOR IN FRONT OF THE BIRTH OF VENUS AND PROPOSED!!! I'm the luckiest!! My sister is going to be so envious!

activities.activityName: Ask partner if they will love me if I was a bug
outcomes: My partner said they would bury me and trample me!! He doesn't like ugly bugs at all! THIS IS THE END!
My partner said that they don't like bugs, but he would find a cure to my curse!
My partner said they would love me on every lifetime! They would become a bug just to love me and nurture me!
I made the mistake of wearing a skirt... And it was all full of ants!! Memories of Vietnam!!! HATE IT!
Standing in the towel wasn't very comfortable, but my partner hold me in their arms caressing my hair!
The food was perfect! The place was perfect! AND THEY PROPOSED!

outcomes: THEY SHOUTED ME! My partner said they hate The Smiths and I had to end it all!
My partner said they've never heard of that indie band, but they will do it for me!
MY PARTNER SAID THEY LOVE THE SMITHS!!! I knew I could trust them!!

It was good I guess... Life is not like the films, but I love them still!

We met their ex... They are more beautiful than me... I HATE IT! I HATE ME!

Their hometown was good, so good really... Maybe we should buy a house
